title: Railworks TS2014 SSS Departmental Hoppers and Wagons Packs
description:
Steam Sounds Supreme Hoppers and Wagons

Departmental Hoppers Pack Features

- Dogfish 24ton Hoppers in 3 liveries
- Catfish 19ton Hoppers in 3 liveries
- Shark Brake Van in bauxite livery
- Custom Sounds


Departmental Wagons Pack Features

- 4 Different Wagon Types in Various Liveries
- Weathered Versions
- Custom Sounds



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.
